PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FA hero hospital patient who talked a
OL,8,F"lone-wolf terrorist" out of
OL,9,Fdetonating a bomb in a maternity wing
OL,10,Fsaid the would-be attacker "asked for
OL,11,Fa cuddle" before telling him to "phone
OL,12,Fthe police before I change my mind".
OL,14,FNathan Newby, who stopped an atrocity
OL,15,Fthrough an act of kindness, spoke
OL,16,Fpublicly for the first time about his
OL,17,Fencounter with Mohammad Farooq ahead
OL,18,Fof receiving the George Medal for
OL,19,Fbravery.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]rD@\OUsD@IO]sD@aOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FFarooq was jailed last year for life
OL,8,Fwith a minimum term of 37 years after
OL,9,Ftaking a home-made pressure cooker
OL,10,Fbomb into St James's Hospital in
OL,11,FLeeds, intending to "kill as many
OL,12,Fnurses as possible".
OL,14,FThe judge who sentenced Farooq, Mrs
OL,15,FJustice Cheema-Grubb, said Mr Newby
OL,16,Fwas "an extraordinary, ordinary man
OL,17,Fwhose decency and kindness on January
OL,18,F20 2023 prevented an atrocity in a
OL,19,Fmaternity wing of a major British
OL,20,Fhospital".
OL,26,@sD@UOUtD@SO]xD@EOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, he will receive the
OL,8,FGeorge Medal ` the second-highest
OL,9,Fcivilian gallantry award ` for his
OL,10,Flifesaving actions.
OL,12,FSpeaking ahead of the ceremony, Mr
OL,13,FNewby, 35, from Leeds, said he thought
OL,14,FFarooq was "probably a nice guy" who
OL,15,Fwas "going through bad things at the
OL,16,Ftime", and saw himself as someone who
OL,17,Fwas "just in the right place at the
OL,18,Fright time".
OL,26,@vD@LOUvD@`O]wD@EOUxD@EO]yD@EOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FA trial heard Farooq had become a
OL,8,F"self-radicalised lone-wolf
OL,9,Fterrorist", inspired by the so-called
OL,10,FIslamic State group, but also chose
OL,11,Fthe hospital as a target as he had
OL,12,Fbeen a clinical support worker there
OL,13,Fand had a long-running grievance with
OL,14,Fnurses on his ward.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FMr Newby, who was a patient at the
OL,8,Fhospital on the night Farooq planned
OL,9,Fto carry out the bombing, said he had
OL,10,Fgone outside for a vape and "a bit of
OL,11,Ffresh air" when he saw Farooq with his
OL,12,Fhands in his pockets, "swaying like
OL,13,Fhe'd had some bad news or something".
OL,15,F"I just went over to see if he was
OL,16,Falright, to see if I could make him
OL,17,Ffeel better," Mr Newby said.
OL,19,F"I said: 'How are you, pal? Are you
OL,20,Falright?' and it just went from there
OL,21,Freally."
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@JO]tD@WOUuD@dO]wD@AOUyD@MO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said Farooq eventually told him he
OL,8,Fwas there "for some sort of revenge,"
OL,9,Fand revealed that he had a bomb about
OL,10,Fan hour into the conversation.
OL,12,F"He was constantly watching (his bag),
OL,13,Fit was about seven foot away from us,
OL,14,Fand every nurse that walked past it,
OL,15,Fhe was like, looking at them, looking
OL,16,Fat the bag.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@eO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,F"And then I asked him what was in
OL,8,Fit... and then he just come out with
OL,9,Fit... he ummed and aahed, didn't want
OL,10,Fto, but then I got out of him. He just
OL,11,Fsaid it's a bomb."
OL,13,FMr Newby said: "I could hear it in his
OL,14,Fvoice, it wasn't a joke, or owt like
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"So I asked to have a look at it, just
OL,18,Fto confirm it, and then he just
OL,19,Fhappily opened it up and showed me it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]uD@POUyD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FMr Newby said "part of me" was scared
OL,8,Fbut that his main concern was to try
OL,9,Fand move Farooq away from the building.
OL,11,F"I wasn't going to shout and things
OL,12,Flike that because it would have been
OL,13,Fnervous for others and just cause
OL,14,Fhavoc, so I just thought, the best way
OL,15,Fis to keep quiet and just get him out
OL,16,Fof the way and be tactical about it."
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@ZO]sD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said he was going through his own
OL,8,Fstruggles with mental health at the
OL,9,Ftime and thought: "If it goes off,
OL,10,Fit's just going to be me and him, and
OL,11,FI want to make sure it's just me and
OL,12,Fhim and not no one else."
OL,14,FHe asked Farooq about the radius and
OL,15,Fmoved him away to some nearby benches,
OL,16,Fworking out that "if it had have gone
OL,17,Foff at least, it would have just took
OL,18,Fthe doors, it wouldn't take the whole
OL,19,Fbuilding out".
OL,26,@qD@SOUtD@YO]xD@ROU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FMr Newby said the plan was "just pure
OL,8,Finstinct," adding: "I don't know where
OL,9,Fit came from."
OL,11,FMr Newby said the pair "just chatted"
OL,12,Fover several hours, with Farooq
OL,13,Ftelling him about his family and
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,F"He asked for a cuddle a few times,
OL,17,Fand I said yeah, of course you can."
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@JO]pD@TOUqD@NO]sD@XOUsD@eO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said Farooq seemed "normal,"
OL,8,Fadding: "I don't judge anybody.
OL,9,FEverybody's different and unique in
OL,10,Ftheir own ways aren't they? I didn't
OL,11,Fjudge him."
OL,13,FMr Newby said that Farooq asked him
OL,14,Ffor a hug and called him a "top guy"
OL,15,Fbefore telling him: "Phone the police
OL,16,Fbefore I change my mind."
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@_O]pD@IOUsD@KO]vD@\OUvD@dO]wD@
OL,26,AUOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said: "It was a bit of a relief,
OL,8,Fbut at the end of the day he could
OL,9,Fhave still changed his mind at any
OL,10,Ftime, even if we were on the phone to
OL,11,Fthe police or not."
OL,13,FMr Newby said the enormity of what had
OL,14,Fhappened did not hit him until he was
OL,15,Fsitting in the back of a police van
OL,16,Fafter armed officers arrived and
OL,17,Fdetained Farooq.
OL,19,F"It started sinking in that it could
OL,20,Fhave been different," he said.
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@SO]{D@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,F"Emotions started coming, it was like
OL,8,Fwow, as if that's just happened."
OL,10,FDuring the phone call to police, Mr
OL,11,FNewby told them Farooq "seemed like a
OL,12,Fnice guy deep down".
OL,14,FAsked how he felt about him now, he
OL,15,Fsaid: "He probably is a nice guy. It
OL,16,Fwas just, his head was in the wrong
OL,17,Fplace at the wrong time.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@aO]sD@XOUtD@SO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,F"I would say he was just going through
OL,8,Fbad things at the time, and when
OL,9,Fyou're in that situation, your mind's
OL,10,Fcapable of doing all sorts of things
OL,11,Fthat you don't expect."
OL,13,FMr Newby said he did not think of
OL,14,Fhimself as a hero, but as someone who
OL,15,Fwas "just in the right place at the
OL,16,Fright time".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]wD@EOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774400571
OL,3,CHero who stopped hospital bombing: 'I
OL,4,Cwas just in the right place at right
OL,5,Ctime'
OL,7,FHe said: "I only think about that
OL,8,Fnight (now) if someone brings it up.
OL,9,FAnd then it's like, it's crazy how it
OL,10,Fcould have gone....I was a patient at
OL,11,Fthe time, so I wouldn't be here,
OL,12,Fbecause I was at the front of the
OL,13,Fbuilding, so it would have took me
OL,14,Fout."
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
